title: The Bat Segundo Show -- Torrent Pack #9
description:
This is the ninth torrent pack of the literary podcast, The Bat Segundo Show, 
which can be found at http://www.edrants.com/segundo.

The podcast features indepth interviews with contemporary authors and is 
hosted by the alcoholic and blacklisted DJ, Bat Segundo.
